# <%= current_page.data.title %>

### Component

An independently deployable piece of software. Synonymous with a microservice, the two terms
are often used interchangeably.

### Platform

A collection of environments, build pipelines, code modules, libraries and tools used to deliver
working software to users.

### Product

A collection of software [components](#component) which form a single line of business. A single product may be
built by multiple [teams](#team) or multiple products may be built by a single team.

### Team

A group of people who build software. It may consist of software engineers,
QAs, infrastructure engineers, testers, scrum master, UX designers, content designers and
many others. A single team may build many [products](#product) or many teams may build a single product.
